src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Midday' game
02 Nov 2019, 17:04 by The Associated Press
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday afternoon's drawing of the Ohio Lottery's "Pick 4 Midday" game were:
9-9-2-4
(nine, nine, two, four)
